Zone name: > 4.60 LAD E. pseudoinflatum <4.9 FAD H. vema
Comments: Small Lithostrobus (one of them similar to B. auritus/australis but without imperforated bands, the other like a compressed P. corbula), Artrostrobus annulatus-like with regular and larger pores, Larcopyle buetschlii

Zone name: > 8.4 LAD A. australis < 8.6 FAD A. strelkovi
Comments: Larcopyle buetschlii, B. auritus/australis without imperforated bands, Acrosphaera murrayana with cylindrical, flared tubes, Short, stout P. bicornis with wings
Acrosphaera murrayana with cylindrical, flared tubes (This is A. australis, fix all over), Artrostrobus annulatus-like with regular and larger pores.
